  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2781210/extras/ede53c77785a15071e99eaf4298fc539.apng?t=1760484679\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2781210/extras/ede53c77785a15071e99eaf4298fc539.poster.avif?t=1760484679\" class=\"bb_img\" width=263 height=71 /></picture></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CAT & ONION is a short adventure game. Find items, talk to to characters and help a friend in need. It's a bit of a fever dream, while also making just enough sense.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as a cat who wakes up with a craving for PANCAKES. However, this quest for pancakes does not go as planned and you have to make a tiny cosmic detour.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game takes 30-60 minutes to complete and I hope it will leave you with a smile.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2781210/extras/5cb36e665d681d7aa86d3b8537a68da8.poster.avif?t=1760484679\" width=616 height=616 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2781210/extras/5cb36e665d681d7aa86d3b8537a68da8.webm?t=1760484679\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2781210/extras/5cb36e665d681d7aa86d3b8537a68da8.mp4?t=1760484679\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2781210/extras/6adacffccf87f984b383815ac619a09c.poster.avif?t=1760484679\" width=251 height=67 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2781210/extras/6adacffccf87f984b383815ac619a09c.webm?t=1760484679\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>You play as a cat!</li><li>Talk, find items and befriend the SPACE ONION</li><li>Meet a cast of entertaining characters</li><li>No combat, unless you count smacking stuff with a baseball bat</li><li>An imaginative world</li><li>Takes 30-60 minutes to finish: You'll experience a lot in a short time!</li><li>A jazzy soundtrack</li><li>Secret cat things for curious cats</li><li>Made by one person</li><li>Enjoy chunky pixelart, with a grand total of 8 colors!</li><li>Cat</li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2781210/extras/ea6787d07b2e84448a65d0cc19bc6163.poster.avif?t=1760484679\" width=616 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2781210/extras/ea6787d07b2e84448a65d0cc19bc6163.webm?t=1760484679\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2781210/extras/ea6787d07b2e84448a65d0cc19bc6163.mp4?t=1760484679\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2781210/extras/ede53c77785a15071e99eaf4298fc539.apng?t=1760484679\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2781210/extras/ede53c77785a15071e99eaf4298fc539.poster.avif?t=1760484679\" class=\"bb_img\" width=263 height=71 /></picture></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CAT & ONION is a short adventure game. Find items, talk to to characters and help a friend in need. It's a bit of a fever dream, while also making just enough sense.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as a cat who wakes up with a craving for PANCAKES. However, this quest for pancakes does not go as planned and you have to make a tiny cosmic detour.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game takes 30-60 minutes to complete and I hope it will leave you with a smile.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2781210/extras/5cb36e665d681d7aa86d3b8537a68da8.poster.avif?t=1760484679\" width=616 height=616 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2781210/extras/5cb36e665d681d7aa86d3b8537a68da8.webm?t=1760484679\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2781210/extras/5cb36e665d681d7aa86d3b8537a68da8.mp4?t=1760484679\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2781210/extras/6adacffccf87f984b383815ac619a09c.poster.avif?t=1760484679\" width=251 height=67 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2781210/extras/6adacffccf87f984b383815ac619a09c.webm?t=1760484679\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>You play as a cat!</li><li>Talk, find items and befriend the SPACE ONION</li><li>Meet a cast of entertaining characters</li><li>No combat, unless you count smacking stuff with a baseball bat</li><li>An imaginative world</li><li>Takes 30-60 minutes to finish: You'll experience a lot in a short time!</li><li>A jazzy soundtrack</li><li>Secret cat things for curious cats</li><li>Made by one person</li><li>Enjoy chunky pixelart, with a grand total of 8 colors!</li><li>Cat</li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2781210/extras/ea6787d07b2e84448a65d0cc19bc6163.poster.avif?t=1760484679\" width=616 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2781210/extras/ea6787d07b2e84448a65d0cc19bc6163.webm?t=1760484679\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2781210/extras/ea6787d07b2e84448a65d0cc19bc6163.mp4?t=1760484679\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
